::Zardus::

Zardus frowns, looking up as the vine shakes again. His scanners report an increase in energon usage. He taps his comm, directing a message at the mass of vines.

"Unknown unit, this is commander Zardus. Please identify yourself."

In a few seconds, a buzzing noise sounds from Zardus's comm, the Alliance commander looking up at the rustling vines in surprise.
